24
00:02:02,090 --> 00:02:04,670
Shall I tell you one more thing I should be congratulated on?

25
00:02:04,670 --> 00:02:08,210
Our party conduced a public opinion poll in Gyeongje City yesterday.

26
00:02:08,210 --> 00:02:12,750
Secretary General, you got 35% and I, 58%.

27
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:18,930
Public opinion is like a lover just before jilting you. Don't count on it too much.

28
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:21,310
Didn't I tell you before

29
00:02:22,130 --> 00:02:26,660
that I would never lose to you, if only for Hyung Dal Soo's sake?

30
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:31,510
I... will trample you.

31
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:37,520
There is a fact that you must be aware of, too.

32
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:43,160
That this inspection is the first and last parliamentary inspection for you.

33
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:46,120
Ah... just one look and I can tell

34
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:50,900
you are brewing some stinking sh*t. I better be careful.

35
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,490
Then.

36
